e%20unemployment%20crisis%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20said%20he%20will%20shortly%20write%20to%20the%20high%20court%20to%20spare%20a%20sitting%20judge%20to%20oversee%20the%20probe.%20The%20promise%20to%20institute%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20scams%20and%20corruption%20against%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(BRS)%20government%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto.%20While%20the%20manifesto%20said%20the%20probe%20would%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20Reddy%20went%20a%20step%20further%2C%20seeking%20a%20sitting%20high%20court%20judge%20to%20go%20into%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%E2%80%99s%20functioning%20has%20been%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20with%20the%20public%20expressing%20outrage%20and%20demanding%20a%20total%20overhaul%20after%20question%20papers%20for%20government%20employment%20were%20repeatedly%20leaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20change%20of%20guard%2C%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20B.%20Janardhan%20Reddy%20submitted%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20when%20governor%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20was%20away%20in%20Puducherry.%20The%20remaining%20five%20members%20are%20expected%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20commission%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20resign%20is%20perceived%20as%20an%20attempt%20at%20a%20%E2%80%98safe%20exit%E2%80%99%20amidst%20a%20series%20of%20blunders%20in%20conducting%20recruitment%20exams%20since%20October%20last%20year%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20protests%20and%20outcry%20from%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resignation%20spree%20has%20given%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20premier%20recruitment%20agency%20for%20state%20services.%20But%20the%20panel%20is%20nervous%20about%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20next%20move.%20Soundararajan%20reportedly%20has%20reservations%20about%20accepting%20the%20resignation%20because%20she%20is%20keen%20on%20fixing%20responsibility%20for%20the%20lapses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20rode%20the%20crest%20of%20a%20wave%20of%20anger%20by%20lakhs%20of%20youth%20who%20were%20anxiously%20looking%20for%20job%20notifications%20under%20the%20BRS%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20conducted%20exams%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20for%20groups%20II%2C%20III%20and%20IV%20services%20but%20the%20group%20I%20notification%20for%20higher%20posts%20was%20not%20issued%20for%20several%20years.%20When%20the%20group%20I%20posts%20were%20finally%20notified%20last%20year%2C%20the%20commission%20received%203.8%20lakh%20applications.%20But%20the%20preliminary%20written%20exam%20in%20October%20was%20cancelled%20after%20two%20persons%20working%20for%20the%20commission%20%E2%80%93%20an%20assistant%20section%20officer%20on%20deputation%20and%20an%20outsourced%20software%20professional%20%E2%80%93%20were%20found%20to%20have%20copied%20the%20question%20papers%20on%20a%20pen%20drive%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20candidates%20for%20a%20huge%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20appointed%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20headed%20by%20the%20additional%20commissioner%20of%20police%20A.R.%20Srinivas%20to%20conduct%20a%20probe.%20The%20team%20arrested%20108%20accused%20persons%2C%20including%20sellers%20and%20buyers%20of%20question%20papers%2C%20and%20filed%20the%20first%20chargesheet%20in%20court.%20The%20second%20chargesheet%20is%20held%20up%20due%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20receipt%20of%20the%20forensic%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20government%20conducted%20the%20preliminary%20written%20exam%20for%20group%20I%20once%20again%20on%20June%207%20this%20year%20but%20this%20was%20again%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-hc-to-tspsc-hold-group-i-prelims-with-biometrics%2Farticleshow%2F104001109.cms%5C%22%3Ecancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20high%20court%20for%20want%20of%20biometric%20attendance%20of%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20group%20II%20exam%20notification%20was%20issued%20but%20it%20was%20postponed%20as%20the%20question%20paper%20was%20leaked%20in%20some%20other%20exams%20of%20the%20commission.%20The%20notification%20for%20the%20group%20III%20exam%20was%20issued%20but%20the%20date%20was%20not%20fixed%20while%20the%20group%20IV%20preliminary%20exam%20was%20taken%20by%20about%207.5%20lakh%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20the%20commission%20cancelled%2016%20written%20exams%20for%20various%20posts%20in%20four%20categories%20comprising%20the%20groups%2C%20departments%20that%20employed%20assistant%20executive%20engineers%2C%20assistant%20engineers%20with%20diplomas%20and%20divisional%20accounts%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20recruitment%20process%20coming%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20the%20frustration%20among%20youth%20waiting%20for%20employment%20mounted.%20Many%20of%20them%20come%20from%20rural%20backgrounds%20and%20lived%20in%20rented%20accommodation%20or%20in%20paying%20guest%20hostels%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20enrol%20in%20coaching%20centres.%20After%20spending%20years%20waiting%20for%20notifications%2C%20they%20returned%20home%20disappointed.%20Their%20struggles%20influenced%20many%20rural%20voters%2C%20who%20felt%20that%20the%20BRS%20government%20was%20indifferent%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20youth.%20The%20death%20by%20suicide%20of%20one%20female%20aspirant%20furthered%20this%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20opposition%20parties%2C%20especially%20the%20Congress%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20aspirants.%20The%20Congress%20came%20up%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98youth%20declaration%E2%80%99%20that%20promised%20two%20lakh%20government%20jobs%20within%20one%20year%20of%20forming%20the%20government.%20All%20backlogs%20for%20people%20from%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%20and%20minority%20communities%20would%20also%20be%20filled%20within%20a%20year%2C%20the%20party%20said%2C%20alongside%20the%20promise%20to%20release%20a%20%E2%80%98job%20calendar%E2%80%99%20on%20June%202%20every%20year%20to%20display%20vacancies%20in%20all%20departments.%20The%20Congress%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20an%20allowance%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20unemployed%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Congress%20also%20annexed%20a%20job%20calendar%20for%202024%20in%20group%20services%20and%20other%20departments%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20also%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20release%20a%20job%20calendar%20to%20fill%20up%20vacancies%20as%20and%20when%20they%20arose.%20Minister%20K.%20T.%20Rama%20Rao%20met%20the%20hostel%20inmates%20at%20Ashok%20Nagar%20in%20Hyderabad%20where%20a%20clutch%20of%20coaching%20centres%20are%20located%20to%20assure%20them%20of%20immediate%20steps%20to%20revive%20the%20recruitment%20process.%20He%20even%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20meet%20them%20on%20December%204%2C%20the%20day%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20election%20results%2C%20to%20draw%20up%20the%20calendar.%20But%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20days%20of%20the%20Congress%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20reviewed%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20at%20an%20official%20meeting.%20It%20was%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20chairman%20and%20members%20of%20the%20commission%20made%20public%20their%20desire%20to%20quit%2C%20apparently%20to%20facilitate%20the%20reorganisation%20of%20the%20commission%20and%20take%20steps%20against%20the%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20Karem%20Ravinder%20Reddy%20said%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20them%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20months%20though%20they%20did%20no%20wrong.%20This%20is%20why%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20members%20decided%20to%20quit.%20Another%20member%2C%20A.%20Satyanarayana%2C%20released%20a%20letter%20to%20youth%20saying%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20members%20spent%20sleepless%20nights%20after%20the%20question%20papers%20were%20leaked.%20Some%20vested%20interests%20wanted%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20commission%20while%20some%20demanded%20the%20removal%20of%20individuals%2C%20he%20claimed.%20It%20was%20untenable%20for%20them%20to%20continue%20due%20to%20their%20mental%20agony%20and%20anguish%2C%20Satyanarayana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20commission%2C%20with%20a%20chairman%20and%20seven%20members%2C%20was%20constituted%20on%20May%2021%2C%202021.%20Two%20members%20retired%20after%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%20retirement%20(62%20years).%20In%20all%2C%20four%20member%20posts%20were%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhanta%20Chakrapani%2C%20a%20former%20chairman%2C%20said%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20commission%20was%20not%20a%20good%20idea.%20The%20Congress%20government%20should%20instead%20fill%20up%20four%20vacancies%20and%20appoint%20one%20of%20them%20as%20the%20in-charge%20chairman%2C%20he%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702643402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15164653%2FGBKRzsKWAAA6EIj.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftelangana-judicial-probe-recruitment-exam-leaks-unemployment-crisis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20all%2C%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20cancelled%2016%20written%20exams%20for%20various%20posts%20in%20four%20categories%20because%20of%20various%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0including%20leakage%20of%20papers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftelangana-judicial-probe-recruitment-exam-leaks-unemployment-crisis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ola's%20Bhavish%20unveils%20K