escribed%20as%20severe%20morning%20sickness%2C%20with%20both%20my%20pregnancies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20my%20experience%20affected%20me%20so%20much%2C%20I've%20been%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20news%20about%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearch%20has%20found%20a%20correlation%20between%20HG%20and%C2%A0GDF15%2C%20a%20hormone%20produced%20by%20a%20growing%20fetus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20ago%20I%20was%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20holidays%20from%20the%20discomfort%20of%20my%20bedroom.%20I%20was%20pregnant%20with%20my%20second%20child%20and%20deeply%20ill.%20I%20threw%20up%20almost%20constantly%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20to%20care%20for%20my%20older%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20would%20take%20her%20to%20preschool%2C%20and%20by%2011%3A30%20a.m.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20drag%20myself%20out%20of%20bed%20and%20get%20in%20the%20car%2C%20one%20way%20or%20another%2C%20to%20go%20pick%20her%20up.%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-is-hyperemesis-gravidarum-symptoms-treatment-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehyperemesis%20gravidarum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20genuinely%20feels%20like%20being%20tortured%20from%20the%20inside%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20to%20me%20was%20a%20plastic%20bag%20I'd%20vomit%20into%20along%20the%20way.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20I'd%20stand%20as%20still%20as%20I%20could%2C%20feeling%20as%20if%20a%20slight%20breeze%20could%20knock%20me%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20too%20sick%20to%20do%20anything%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%203-year-old%20daughter%2C%20Piper%2C%20and%20I%20got%20home%2C%20I'd%20let%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-screen-time-affects-childrens-brains-nih-study-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20hadn't%20done%20much%20of%20until%20then%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0while%20I%20rested.%20Eventually%20she'd%20get%20bored%2C%20I'd%20run%20a%20bath%2C%20and%20we'd%20climb%20in%20together.%20She'd%20play%20with%20toys%20while%20I%20closed%20my%20eyes%20and%20begged%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwoman-had-hyperemesis-gravidarum-diagnosed-after-several-doctor-visits-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20sickness%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fade%20or%20for%20my%20husband%20to%20get%20home%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20make%20cookies%20that%20year%20or%20attend%20holiday%20gatherings.%20I%20was%20too%20sick%20to%20talk%20to%20people.%20Most%20days%20I%20felt%20too%20sick%20to%20be%20inside%20my%20own%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20had%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20older%20child%20during%20my%20second%20pregnancy%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20bit%20less%20jarred%20because%20I%20knew%20what%20was%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20had%20it%20with%20both%20of%20my%20pregnancies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20first%20pregnancy%2C%20I%20lost%2020%20pounds.%20Doctors%20looked%20at%20me%20perplexed%20each%20time%20the%20scale%20moved%20backward.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20failure%20of%20a%20woman%20that%20I%20couldn't%20handle%20%26quot%3Bmorning%20sickness%2C%26quot%3B%20something%20almost%20everyone%20went%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20HG%20isn't%20morning%20sickness%3B%20it's%20a%20whole%20other%20beast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20found%20out%20I%20was%20pregnant%20again%2C%20I%20was%20terrified%20of%20what%20I%20knew%20would%20most%20likely%20set%20in.%20I%20started%20nausea%20medication%20right%20away%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20take%20the%20edge%20off%20until%20about%20week%2015%20%E2%80%94%20when%20I%20finally%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20down%20food%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%2010%20years%20since%20I%20last%20suffered%20through%20HG%2C%20but%20I%20still%20follow%20research%20on%20the%20illness%20closely%2C%20hoping%20that%20soon%20there%20will%20be%20better%20help%20for%20women%20who%20spend%20weeks%20and%20months%20debilitated%20by%20their%20pregnancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFinally%20there's%20an%20explanation%20for%20HG%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20a%20story%20came%20across%20my%20feed%20that%20made%20me%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20long%20been%20chatter%20that%20HG%20is%20caused%20by%20fluctuating%20hormones.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da2874951c443b590883e8d96a6d7e1cc7146b5e77663ad94a5501cd6acea0cc7%26postID%3D657b3a8c8d7dad6fbf27e9d0%26postSlug%3Dsuffered-through-hyperemesis-gravidarum-twice-what-it-was-like-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41586-023-06921-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20scientists%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20suggests%20that%20how%20sick%20a%20person%20will%20become%20has%20to%20do%20with%20their%20sensitivity%20to%20GDF15%2C%20a%20hormone%20a%20growing%20fetus%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20found%20that%20women%20with%20genetic%20variants%20of%20GDF15%20linked%20with%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20developing%20HG%20had%20lower%20levels%20of%20the%20hormone%20when%20they%20weren't%20pregnant.%20Women%20with%20a%20blood%20disorder%20associated%20with%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20hormone%20reported%20very%20little%20sickness%20during%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20is%20groundbreaking%20because%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20scientists%20feel%20they've%20found%20a%20cause.%20That%20means%20they%20can%20start%20working%20on%20a%20cure.%20Researchers%20involved%20in%20the%20study%20have%20suggested%20that%20exposure%20to%20the%20hormone%20before%20pregnancy%20could%20help%20women%20like%20me%20who%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20developing%20HG%20avoid%20going%20through%20the%20sickness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHaving%20HG%20was%20pure%20misery%20for%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20woman%20who's%20gone%20through%20weeks%20or%20months%20of%20endless%20vomiting%20and%20nausea%20understands%20how%20truly%20terribl