of%20South%20Indian-Origin%20Social%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15162605%2FUntitled-design.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CPropagating%20religion%20and%20promoting%20good%20things%20about%20religion%20is%20not%20a%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sonbhadra%20district%20noted%20on%20December%2014%20as%20it%20granted%20bail%20to%20six%20persons%2C%20including%20two%20south%20Indian-origin%20social%20workers%2C%20accused%20of%20converting%20lower%20caste%20and%20marginalised%20members%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20to%20Christianity%20through%20allurements%20and%20inducements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20police%20in%20eastern%20UP%20have%20arrested%20at%20least%20four%20persons%20hailing%20from%20south%20Indian%20states%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20convert%20backward%20caste%20and%20tribal%20Hindus%20through%20allurements%20of%20providing%20them%20a%20better%20life%20and%20free%20education%20and%20health%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20case%2C%20lodged%20in%20the%20backward%20Sonbhadra%20district%2C%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20an%20office-bearer%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20police%20booked%2042%20persons%20under%20Sections%203%20and%205%20(1)%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021.%20Nine%20persons%2C%20including%20a%20person%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20one%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20were%20arrested.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20police%20in%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20on%20December%2011%20arrested%20a%20couple%20originally%20from%20Kerala%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20alluring%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20backward%20caste%20Nishad%20community%20to%20convert%20and%20for%20insulting%20Hindu%20deities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20creating%20a%20situation%20of%20caste%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narsingh%20Tripathi%2C%20the%20VHP%20activist%20who%20lodged%20the%20police%20complaint%20in%20Sonbhadra%2C%20told%20The%20Wire%20on%20what%20motivated%20him%20to%20file%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20Chopan%20police%20station%20in%20Sonbhadra%20on%20Tripathi%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20were%20trying%20to%20convert%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebholi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ebhali%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(na%C3%AFve)%20and%20deprived%20people%20living%20in%20the%20tribal%20dominated%20areas.%20They%20were%20also%20afflicted%20by%20superstition%2C%20Tripathi%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20named%2042%20persons%20including%20Christian%20social%20workers%20Jai%20Prabhu%2C%20Chheka%20Emmanuel%20and%20K%20Sojanya.%20Prabhu%2C%2040%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20hails%20from%20Chennai%20and%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Sonbhadra%20since%202011%20after%20he%20came%20to%20a%20local%20church.%C2%A0%20Chekka%20Emmanuel%20and%20his%20wife%20K.%20Sojanya%20hail%20from%20Vijaywada%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20but%20have%20been%20residents%20of%20Sonbhadra%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbjp-sikandar-bakht-love-jihad%5C%22%3EEven%20Sikandar%20Bakht%2C%20BJP%20Posterboy%20of%20Yesteryears%2C%20Would%20Know%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20Is%20Only%20a%20Ruse%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20include%20pastors%20Sanjay%20John%2C%20Chotu%20Ranjan%2C%20Sohanram%20and%20Sant%20Lal%20Gond%2C%20Prakash%20HL%20Marandi%20(a%20teacher%20of%20St.%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20school%20Shaktinagar%2C%20a%20co-educational%20English%20Medium%20School%2C%20established%20in%201978%2C%20and%20managed%20by%20the%20Roman%20Catholic%20Diocese%20of%20Allahabad%20Education%20Society)%2C%20sanitation%20workers%20Durgawati%20Devi%20and%20Parmanand%2C%20and%20priest%20Fr.%20Paras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20accused%20belong%20to%20the%20Dalit%2C%20OBC%20and%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20accused%20them%20of%20helping%20poor%20tribals%20financially%2C%20and%20distributing%20money%20and%20other%20essential%20items%20among%20them%20in%20order%20to%20get%20them%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20misled%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20and%20illiterate%20people%E2%80%9D%20by%20providing%20their%20children%20free%20education%2C%20free%20school%20uniforms%2C%20free%20books%20and%20do%20%3Cem%3Ejhaad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3Ephoonk%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20style%20of%20exorcism)%20to%20cure%20them%20of%20ailments%20at%20%3Cem%3Echangai%20sabhas%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eheld%20every%20Sunday%2C%20he%20alleged%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Tripathi%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20provided%20free%20treatment%20in%20Christian%20hospitals%20and%20while%20doing%20so%20gave%20the%20public%20from%20the%20tribal%20areas%20allurements%20to%20make%20them%20believe%20that%20%E2%80%9CJesus%20Christ%20is%20the%20only%20Eshwar%20(lord)%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CChristian%20faith%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20kalyan%20(welfare).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20such%20allurements%20and%20promises%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(the%20people)%20are%20psychologically%20mesmerized%20towards%20conversion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonbhadra%20police%20ASP%20(headquarters)%20Kalu%20Singh%20said%20the%20natives%20of%20Southern%20states%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20Sonbhadra%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Nine%20out%20of%20the%2042%20had%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20claimed%20they%20had%20recovered%20over%20100%20religious%20items%20used%20by%20the%20accused%20to%20convert%20people.%20These%20included%2010%20copies%20of%20the%20Bible%2C%2013%20holy%20scriptures%2C%20307%20prayer%20pamphlets%2C%20five%20talking%20Bible%20audio%20tapes%2C%20a%20convention%20song%20CD%20and%20other%20prayer%20books%2C%20including%20one%20named%20%E2%80%98UP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20liye%20prarthana%20pushtak%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(A%20book%20of%20prayer%20for%20UP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20Chopan%20area%2C%20the%20accused%20were%20spread%20across%20the%20district%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20be%20mineral-rich%20and%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FZW9JxoJ6KOg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Two%20Churches%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Targeted%20by%20Right%20Wing%20Group%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98What%20motive%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20unearthed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cweb%E2%80%9D%20of%20illegal%20conversion.%20While%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20an%20office-bearer%20of%20the%20VHP%2C%20he%20said%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20motive%20did%20they%20have%20in%20coming%20to%20Sonbhadra%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Chennai%20and%20other%20southern%20states%3F%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20here%20for%20a%20job%20or%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20why%20he%20accused%20Jai%20Prabhu%2C%20Emmanuel%20Chekka%20and%20K.%20Sojanya%20of%20illegal%20conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20bail%20applications%2C%20Prabhu%2C%20Emmanuel%20and%20four%20others%20said%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20them%20were%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cimaginary%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20misusing%20the%20anti-conversion%20law.%20They%20argued%20that%20the%20complainant%20Tripathi%20nor%20his%20family%20nor%20anyone%20else%20had%20been%20converted%20by%20them.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20anyone%20who%20was%20converted.%20The%20complainant%20considers%20himself%20thekadar%20of%20the%20dharm%C2%A0(contractor%20of%20the%20Hindu%20faith)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20accused%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhu%20and%20Emmanuel%20told%20the%20court%20they%20were%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESessions%20judge%2C%20Sonbhadra%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Yadav%20granted%20them%20bail%2C%20observing%20that%20at%20this%20stage%20it%20did%20not%20appear%20that%20the%20accused%20converted%20people%20by%20force%20or%20against%20their%20wishes.%20It%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20be%20said%20with%20certainty%E2%80%9D%20that%20they%20deceived%20people%20through%20inducements%20to%20leave%20their%20religion%20and%20adopt%20the%20Christian%20faith%2C%20judge%20Yadav%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20commented%20on%20the%20religious%20material%20seized%20from%20the%20accused%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20not%20against%20the%20law%20for%20a%20person%20who%20followed%20a%20religion%20to%20have%20in%20his%20or%20her%20possession%20religious%20material%20related%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Free%20tuition%20classes%20in%20a%20Brahminical%20system%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aide%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20Wire%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20the%20VHP%20activist%20had%20no%20%3Cem%3Elocus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Estandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20lodging%20an%20FIR%20when%20those%20who%20were%20allegedly%20converted%20had%20not%20complained%20to%20the%20police.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20this%20means%20we%20have%20no%20right%20to%20even%20propagate%20our%20religion%3F%20People%20come%20to%20these%20sabhas%20on%20their%20own%20will.%20Nobody%20forces%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20feels%20the%20VHP%20targeted%20them%20because%20the%20sabhas%20were%20making%20SCs%20and%20STs%20in%20the%20area%20aware%20about%20their%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20main%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20should%20remain%20the%20way%20they%20were%2C%20that%20is%20under%20control%20of%20the%20Brahmanical%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20clarifying%20that%20those%20who%20attended%20these%20prayer%20meets%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20formally%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20continue%20to%20follow%20their%20Hindu%20culture.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20follow%20their%20indigenous%20culture%20and%20Hindu%20faith%20but%20have%20Jesus%20in%20their%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdistributing-bibles-encouraging-childrens-education-not-allurement%5C%22%3EDistributing%20The%20Bible%2C%20Encouraging%20Education%20Not%20%E2%80%98Allurement%E2%80%99%20for%20Conversion%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20as%20well%20as%20local%20police%20said%20that%20Prabhu%20and%20Emmanuel%2C%20who%20Tripathi%20has%20accused%20as%20being%20%E2%80%9Cringmasters%E2%80%9D%20of%20unlawful%20conversion%2C%20gave%20free%20tuition%20lessons%20to%20underprivileged%20children%20and%20helped%20their%20families%20with%20free%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESHO%20Chopan%C2%A0Vishwanath%20Pratap%20Singh%20said%20while%20nine%20persons%20were%20arrested%2C%20they%20were%20gathering%20more%20evidence%20against%20possible%20others%20of%20the%20others.%C2%A0%20Police%20were%20recording%20statements%20of%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20witnesses%E2%80%9D%20who%20were%20allegedly%20converted%20at%20these%20meetings%20and%20gathering%20%E2%80%9Csupporting%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Tripathi%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20Singh%20said.%20The%20accused%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnetwork%20in%20the%20entire%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyajeet%20Gupta%2C%20SP%20of%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%2C%20said%20a%20case%20had%20been%20registered%20at%20Khalilabad%20police%20station%20against%20Jose%20Pulluvelil%20and%20Elma%20Pulluvelil%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Pathanamthitta%20district%20of%20Kerala%2C%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20one%20Nirmala%20Nishad%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20assured%20her%20that%20she%20would%20find%20her%20son%2C%20who%20was%20missing%20since%20three%20years%2C%20if%20she%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20Nishad%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20used%20insulting%20language%20for%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20tore%20her%20kalava%20(religious%20threat%20worn%20on%20the%20wrist)%20and%20removed%20her%20mangalsutra%20and%20bichiya%20(toe%20ring).%20Nishad%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20would%20induce%20people%20from%20Dalit%20communities%20to%20convert%20in%20the%20prarthna%20sabhas%20(prayer%20meetings)%20held%20in%20her%20village%20every%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20said%20the%20couple%20was%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20after%20their%20statements%20were%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETextbook%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonbhadra%20case%2C%20though%20one%20among%20the%20hundreds%20of%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20UP%20under%20the%20anti-conversion%20law%20since%202020%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20what%20a%20forceful%20conversion%20is%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20state.%20In%20August%202021%2C%20seven%20months%20after%20the%20state%20government%20introduced%20a%20stringent%20new%20law%20against%20unlawful%20conversion%2C%20it%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20providing%20two%20illustrations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20conversion%E2%80%9D%20in%20response%20to%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20constitutional%20validity%20of%20the%20law.%20One%20of%20the%20illustrations%20involved%20inter-faith%20marriages%20involving%20Hindu%20women.%20The%20second%20one%20was%20about%20Christian%20missionaries%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20convert%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20talked%20about%20a%20group%20of%20Christian%20missionaries%20visiting%20a%20Dalit%20busty%20to%20allure%20every%20member%20of%20the%20community%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20if%20they%20started%20believing%20in%20God%20or%20started%20reading%20the%20Bible%2C%20they%20would%20be%20provided%20with%20a%20free%20training%20course%20as%20a%20nurse%20and%20later%20a%20job%20in%20a%20hospital.%20The%20missionaries%20allure%20them%20to%20leave%20their%20faith%20based%20on%20these%20assurances.%C2%A0The%20Dalits%20leaving%20their%20faith%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20assurances%2C%C2%A0amounts%20to%20a%20forced%C2%A0conversion%2C%20the%20state%20government%20informed%20the%20HC.%20The%20Dalits%20in%20this%20case%20did%20not%20have%20a%20freedom%20of%20choice%20but%20their%20choice%20was%C2%A0obtained%20by%20certain%20allurement%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702639802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15162605%2FUntitled-design.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-religious-conversion-south-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20police%20in%20eastern%20UP%20have%20arrested%20at%20least%20four%20persons%20hailing%20from%20south%20Indian%20states%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20convert%20backward%20caste%20and%20tribal%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-religious-conversion-south-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Murder%20Accused%20Shot%20Dead%20In%20Patna%20Court%20Complex%20In%20Front%20Of%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20undertrial%20prisoner%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20two%20men%20in%20a%20court%20complex%20in%20Patna%20on%20Friday.%20Both%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Kumar%20alias%20Chhote%20Sarkar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Sikanderpur%2C%20faced%20murder%20charges%20among%20several%20other%20cases.%20He%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20city's%20Beur%20jail%20and%20was%20to%20be%20presented%20before%20the%20court%20today%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20Danapur%20court%20when%20two%20men%20attacked%20him%20and%20he%20was%20shot%20dead.%20The%20attackers%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20They%20will%20be%20interrogated%20to%20ascertain%20who%20sent%20them%20and%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patna%20West%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Rajesh%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20caught%20hold%20of%20the%20two%20accused%20and%20tackled%20them%20down%20right%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20showed%20visuals.%20Later%2C%20they%20were%20seen%20being%20dragged%20away%20by%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20bullet%20shells%20have%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20area%20and%20the%20situation%20remains%20tense%20in%20the%20court%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20attackers%20are%20from%20Muzaffarpur.%20The%20police%20have%20found%20four%20shells%2C%20but%20it%20is%20unclear%20how%20many%20bullets%20hit%20the%20undertrial%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20police%20officer%20was%20shot%20dead%20and%20another%20was%20seriously%20injured%20outside%20the%20Danapur%20court%20when%20a%20group%20of%20men%20attacked%20a%20police%20team%20escorting%20undertrial%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702639740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fsedjieeg_patna-court-firing_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpatna-news%2Fundertrial-pr