in-america-67638183.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Govt%20Tells%20SC%20it%20Will%20Follow%20CBI%20Manual%20on%20Device%20Seizure.%20Here's%20What%20the%20Manual%20Says.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15141230%2Feirik-solheim-mWTOR3Rx8l8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20on%20Thursday%20sought%20yet%20another%20adjournment%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20hearing%20petitions%20on%20device%20seizures%2C%20on%20the%20excuse%20that%20its%20committee%20was%20still%20discussing%20suitable%20guidelines%20on%20the%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20phones%20and%20other%20electronic%20devices.%20Even%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20orally%20expressed%20discomfort%20at%20the%20repeated%20adjournments%20sought%20by%20the%20government%2C%20it%20recorded%20the%20statement%20of%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20representing%20the%20government%2C%20that%20the%20Union%20agencies%20will%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20Manual%202020%20on%20search%20and%20seizure%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20while%20giving%20government%20a%20further%20time%20of%20six%20weeks%20to%20finalise%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20who%20is%20about%20to%20demit%20office%20later%20this%20month%2C%20and%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20was%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20writ%20petitions%20including%20one%20brought%20by%20well-known%20academics%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20M.%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Mukul%20Kesavan%20and%20Deepak%20Malghan%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20and%20another%20brought%20by%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Siddharth%20Agrawal.%20The%20matter%20is%20set%20to%20come%20up%20next%20for%20hearing%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20since%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20review%20some%20of%20the%20guidelines%20proposed%20as%20interim%20guidelines%20by%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20CBI%20Manual%2C%202020%2C%20which%20bears%20a%20%E2%80%98Restricted%E2%80%99%20classification%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20agencies%20will%20now%20have%20to%20observe%20procedures%20such%20as%20generation%20of%20hash%20value%20for%20each%20device%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%20of%20such%20devices%2C%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20the%20seizure%20memo.%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20of%20the%20guidelines%20suggested%20by%20the%20petitioners%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%5Bt%5Dhe%20chain%20of%20custody%20of%20the%20material%20must%20be%20maintained%2C%20and%20the%20hash%20values%20of%20the%20devices%20must%20be%20recorded%20and%20verified%20at%20each%20transition.%20Each%20step%20must%20be%20documented%20and%20explained%20so%20that%20a%20third%20party%20should%20be%20able%20to%20replicate%20the%20process%20and%20arrive%20at%20the%20same%20result.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20requirement%20is%20provided%20for%20under%20the%20manual%20detailing%20procedures%20of%20hash%20value%20generation%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20recording%20of%20the%20same%20in%20the%20seizure%20memo%2C%20the%20opening%20of%20chain%20of%20custody%20reports%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20and%20the%20hash%20value%20and%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20reports%20being%20made%20available%20along%20with%20the%20devices%20to%20the%20forensic%20laboratory%20(Sections%2016.19%20and%2016.23).%20The%20importance%20attached%20to%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20is%20underlined%20in%20Section%2012.24%20where%20it%20says%20%E2%80%9C%5Bi%3Cem%3E%5Df%20it%20is%20not%20properly%20maintained%2C%20an%20item%20may%20become%20inadmissible%20in%20the%20court.%20Failure%20to%20substantiate%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20may%20lead%20to%20serious%20questions%20regarding%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20evidence%20and%20the%20examination%20rendered%20upon%20it%2C%20making%20the%20whole%20process%20as%20an%20exercise%20in%20futility.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20suggestion%20that%20the%20evidence%20obtained%20without%20scrupulously%20following%20these%20safeguards%20to%20ordinarily%20not%20be%20admitted%20against%20any%20person%20accused%20of%20an%20offence%20in%20criminal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20provision%20in%20the%20manual%20is%20the%20requirement%20of%20the%20investigating%20agency%20to%20avoid%20indiscriminate%20seizure.%20Section%209.12%20of%20the%20manual%20states%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3Ethere%20should%20be%20no%20indiscriminate%20seizure%20of%20documents%20in%20any%20case.%20It%20should%20be%20borne%20in%20mind%20that%20seizure%20of%20records%20may%20cause%20dislocation%20of%20work%20in%20the%20office%20concerned.%20Hence%2C%20records%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20into%20possession%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20routine.%20The%20IO%20should%20seize%2Frequisition%20the%20records%20only%20if%20the%20same%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20investigation.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20examination%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20records%20on%20the%20spot%20might%20suffice%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Petitioners%20have%20suggested%20that%20no%20seizure%20or%20search%20of%20personal%20digital%20device%20be%20effected%20without%20a%20judicial%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20was%20mentioned%20in%20court%20on%20Thursday%2C%20ASG%20Raju%20expressed%20a%20severe%20disagreement%20and%20spoke%20of%20leakages%20as%20though%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20search%20warrant%20was%20inimical%20to%20law%20enforcement.%20He%20was%20perhaps%2C%20unmindful%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20itself%20makes%20obtainment%20of%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20%E2%80%98preferable%E2%80%99%20before%20search.%20If%20it%20is%20to%20be%20followed%2C%20the%20agency%20would%20presumably%20have%20to%20justify%20any%20breach%20of%20the%20preferred%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20other%20key%20demands%20of%20the%20petitioners%20remain%20unmet%20by%20the%20CBI%20Manual.%20The%20Manual%20also%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20any%20safeguards%20relating%20to%20passwords%2Fcredentials%20coercion%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20device%20owner%20during%20examination%20of%20the%20devices%20or%20data%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20segregation%20privileged%20material%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20journalistic%20material%2C%20privileged%20correspondence%20such%20as%20between%20an%20attorney%20and%20a%20client%2C%20or%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient%2C%20communications%20between%20spouses%20as%20also%20all%20irrelevant%20and%20personal%20material.%20Other%20than%20deprecating%20any%20%E2%80%9Cindiscriminate%20seizure%20of%20documents%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20does%20not%20make%20any%20provision%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20not%20done.%20Yet%2C%20agencies%20must%20now%20be%20mindful%20of%20this%20principle%2C%20which%20they%20have%20all%20along%20been%20ignoring%20till%20date%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20asks%20is%20a%20definitive%20guideline%20on%20timelines%20for%20return%20of%20digital%20devices%2C%20and%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20addressed%20in%20the%20CBI%20Manual%2C%20although%20it%20has%20a%20general%20directive%20for%20expeditious%20return%20of%20seized%20material%20(whether%20digital%20or%20otherwise)%20in%20Section%209.16.%20However%2C%20this%20concern%20may%20somewhat%20be%20mitigated%20by%20the%20mandate%20under%20Section%209.41%20that%20investigation%20should%20be%20carried%20out%20only%20on%20the%20mirror%20image%20of%20the%20data%20obtained%20from%20the%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20thereby%20obviating%20the%20need%20for%20the%20investigation%20agencies%20to%20retain%20the%20devices%20after%20the%20mirroring%20process%20is%20complete.%C2%A0%20It%20may%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20Section%209.16%20of%20the%20Manual%20lays%20down%20an%20outer%20limit%20of%20a%20fortnight%20for%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20CBI%20report%20and%20mandate%20the%20obtaining%20of%20orders%20from%20the%20magistrate%20under%20Section%20457%20of%20the%20CrPC%20for%20disposal%20or%20return%20of%20seized%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20this%2C%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20the%20court%20is%20certainly%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20bringing%20some%20discipline%20to%20investigation%20practices%20around%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20personal%20digital%20devices.%C2%A0%20Investigating%20agencies%20are%20not%20known%20to%20observe%20many%20of%20these%20safeguards.%20Reportage%20on%20the%20recent%20cases%20involving%20the%20founding%20editors%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-journalists-seized-press-freedom-delhi-court-the-wire%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20journalists%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20testament%20to%20this.%20For%20instance%2C%20neither%20were%20hash%20value%20reports%20provided%20at%20the%20time%20of%20seizure%2C%20nor%20were%20the%20devices%20returned%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20to%20the%20device%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702636226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15141230%2Feirik-solheim-mWTOR3Rx8l8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-tells-sc-it-will-follow-cbi-manual-on-device-seizure-heres-what-the-manual-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20has%20promised%20to%20follow%20the%20CBI%20Manual%20while%20it%20works%20on%20preparing%20guidelines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-tells-sc-it-will-follow-cbi-manual-on-device-seizure-heres-what-the-manual-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20signs%20you%20have%20a%20Golden%20Retriever%20boyfriend%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20the%20bar%20for%20men%20is%20so%20low%20in%20relationships%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Travis%20Kelce%20walking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579df537a3c8094d5dc8eb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravis%20Kelce's%20energy%20toward%20Taylor%20Swift%20has%20led%20fans%20to%20label%20him%20a%20Golden%20Retriever%20boyfriend%3Cp%3EGotham%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGolden%20Retriever%20boyfriends%20are%20the%20hottest%20trend%20in%20dating%20right%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20are%20sweet%2C%20affectionate%2C%20and%20attentive%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20the%20beloved%20dog%20breed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%A0But%20a%20therapist%20said%20these%20are%20very%20basic%20expectations%20in%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20trends%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsituationship-dating-trend-young-singles-relationship-status-gen-z-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20situationships%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fghosting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eghosting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fbreadcrumbing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebreadcrumbing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20make%20modern%20romance%20feel%20depressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20that's%20why%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20Golden%20Retriever%20boyfriend%2C%20a%20man%20with%20personality%20traits%20that%20resemble%20the%20reliable%20and%20friendly%20beloved%20dog%20breed%2C%20has%20caught%20people's%20attention%20recently%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20straight%20women.%20The%20concept%20first%20popped%20up%20on%20TikTok%20in%202021%20and%20recently%20exploded%20online%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-relationship-timeline-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETaylor%20Swift%20and%20Travis%20Kelce%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(widely%20considered%20a%20classic%20GRB)%20became%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20seems%20positive%20overall%20to%20Dr.%20Annie%20Zimmerman%2C%20a%20psychotherapist%20based%20in%20London%2C%20who%20shares%20psychology%20and%20relationship%20advice%20online%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyour_pocket_therapist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYour%20Pocket%20Therapist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20a%20Golden%20Retriever%20boyfriend%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20understanding%20is%20it's%20quite%20a%20positive%20thing.%20A%20man%20who's%20just%20nice%20and%20really%20caring%20of%20their%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimmerman%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20upcoming%20book%20%26quot%3BYour%20Pocket%20Therapist%3A%20Break%20Free%20from%20Old%20Patterns%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20just%20always%20present%20and%20excited%20to%20see%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20Zimmerman%2C%20it%20also%20highlights%20a%20sad%20reality%20about%20dating.%20%26quot%3BI%20found%20it%20quite%20sad%20in%20a%20way%20that%20in%20the%20modern%20dating%20times%20we're%20in%20just%20a%20nice%20person%20is%20being%20labeled%20as%20a%20Golden%20Retriever%2C%20as%20if%20it's%20so%20rare%20to%20have%20a%20person%20who's%20affectionate%20and%20loving%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20trend%20puts%20a%20spotlight%20on%20men%20who%20are%20sensitive%2C%20gentle%2C%20and%20emotionally%20open%2C%20and%20offers%20a%20welcome%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bbad%20boy%26quot%3B%20trope%2C%20these%20are%20basic%20requirements%20for%20a%20partner%20to%20have%20in%20a%20healthy%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZimmerman%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20men%20who%20are%20attentive%20and%20considerate%20are%20deemed%20remarkable%2C%20while%20women%20are%20simply%20expected%20to%20embody%20these%20traits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20aren't%20we%20speaking%20of%20Golden%20Retriever%20girlfriends%3F%20Would%20they%20be%20seen%20as%20clingy%20or%20needy%20for%20being%20friendly%20and%20attentive%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20many%20women%20needed%20men%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpartner-career-job-success-jealousy-relationship-2023-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20for%20them%20financially%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20today%20they're%20looking%20for%20something%20very%20different.%20They%20want%20someone%20who%20is%20emotionally%20mature%20and%20can%20boost%20them%20up%2C%20which%20comes%20from%20having%20a%20loving%2C%20positive%2C%20and%20happy%20partner%2C%20Zimmerman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20finding%20that%20with%20men%20they're%20not%20getting%20what%20they%20want.%20They're%20in%20situationships%20or%20they're%20being%20ghosted%20and%20you%20have%20to%20work%20quite%20hard%20to%20find%20someone%20who%20treats%20you%20nicely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you're%20curious%20whether%20you're%20with%20one%20of%20these%20mystical%20men%2C%20or%20want%20to%20know%20what%20to%20look%20out%20for%2C%20here%20are%20eight%20traits%20of%20a%20Golden%20Retriever%20Boyfriend%20AKA%20a%20nice%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGolden%20Retriever%20boyfriend%20personality%20traits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EThey're%20attentive%2C%20eager%20to%20please%2C%20and%20enjoy%20doing%20things%20for%20you%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20can%20be%20very%20positive%20traits%20if%20they're%20coming%20from%20a%20healthy%20desire%20to%20want%20to%20love%20your%20partner%20the%20best%20way%20that%20you%20can%2C%20Zimmerman%20said%2C%20but%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20known%20as%20acts%20of%20service%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20planning%20an%20elaborate%20date%20or%20doing%20the%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20gift-giving%20are%20two%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Flove-languages%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efive%20love%20languages%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20concept%20that%20categorizes%20how%20people%20prefer%20to%20give%20and%20receive%20love%2C%20and%20wanting%20to%20meet%20your%20partner's%20needs%20is%20a%20part%20of%20any%20healthy%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20being%20eager%20to%20please%20or%20overly%20attentive%20can%20also%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-stop-being-a-people-pleaser-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20pleasing%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20being%20able%20to%20say%20no%2C%20or%20not%20being%20able%20to%20express%20a%20negative%20feeling%20or%20a%20difference%20in%20opinion%2C%20Zimmerman%20said.%20That%20can%20easily%20lead%20to%20resentment%20and%20the%20sacrificing%20of%20your%20own%20needs%20for%20the%20other%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThey're%20affectionate%2C%20loving%2C%20and%20sweet%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20is%20used%20to%20being%20treated%20badly%20or%20feels%20deep%20down%20that%20it's%20what%20they%20deserve%20due%20to%20low%20self-esteem%2C%20they%20may%20be%20attracted%20to%20that%20kind%20of%20treatment%20because%20it's%20familiar%2C%20Zimmerman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20the%20aim%20is%