%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20feel%20safe%20here.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20road.%20It's%20a%20basic%20human%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20outside%20in%20the%20open%20air.%20All%20these%20women%20in%20your%20office%2C%20can%20you%20guys%20walk%20on%20the%20street%3F%20Isn't%20that%20sad%3F%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20sit%20in%20a%20car.%20I%20want%20to%20cycle.%20Why%20can't%20I%20ride%20a%20bike%3F%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Omar%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2449777%2Fi-dont-feel-safe-here-ayesha-omar-opens-up-on-barriers-to-womens-freedom%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Express%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20also%20emphasised%20that%20men%20may%20never%20fully%20comprehend%20the%20constant%20fear%20and%20anxiety%20that%20women%20deal%20with%20daily.%20%26quot%3BMen%20can%20never%20understand%20what%20Pakistani%20women%20grow%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20you%20try%2C%20you%20cannot.%20Because%20that%20fear%20that%20a%20woman%20has%20in%20this%20country%20-%20sure%2C%20he%20who%20has%20daughters%20may%20understand.%20Being%20in%20a%20woman's%20shoes%20and%20understanding%20that%20is%20impossible.%20You're%20anxious%20every%20second%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftom-cruise-spotted-partying-with-russian-socialite-elsina-khayrova-all-you-need-to-know-about-her-4674097%5C%22%3ETom%20Cruise%20Spotted%20Partying%20With%20Russian%20Socialite%20Elsina%20Khayrova%2C%20All%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%20About%20Her%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Omar%20recounted%20her%20encounter%20with%20harassment%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BMy%20earliest%20encounter%20with%20harassment%20was%20when%20my%20neighbour's%20cook%20touched%20me%20inappropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shared.%20The%20actor%20t