ily%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20marriage%20was%20instilled%20in%20her%20mind%20very%20young%2C%20%C2%A0she%20was%20also%20%E2%80%9Cmadly%20in%20love%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20When%20Urvashi%20was%20asked%20why%20she%20got%20married%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYeah%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%20I%20was%20madly%20in%20love.%20Even%20if%20you%20ask%20me%20today%20won't%20deny%20that.%20Yes%2C%20love%20was%20there%20that%20is%20why%20I%20left%20everything%20to%20explore%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world.%20And%20we%20come%20from%20that%20era%2C%20where%20the%20constitution%20of%20marriage%20is%20instilled%20in%20you%2C%20as%20a%20woman%E2%80%A6as%20a%20girl%20child.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20say%20that%20I%20come%20from%20an%20old%20time%2C%20but%20as%20I%20said%2C%20I%20was%20born%20to%20elderly%20parents%20and%20my%20mother%20being%20a%20conservative%20Punjabi%20woman%2C%20it%20was%20all%20instilled.%20Society%20was%20like%20that%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time.%20And%20then%20I%20realised%20that%20what%20am%20I%20doing%3F%E2%80%9D%20Urvashi%20Dholakia%20said%20that%20she%20was%20just%2016%20and%20not%20mature%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20in%20the%20constitution%20of%20marriage.%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20it.%20I%20was%2016%20and%20was%20not%20mature%20enough.%20But%20at%20that%20time%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%20Urvashi%20Dholakia%20continued%20by%20revealing%20that%20she%20had%20known%20her%20former%20husband%20for%20almost%20one-and-a-half%20years%20before%20marriage.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20like%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20work%20now%2C%20I%20want%20a%20Cinderella%20life%20now.%20But%20then%20the%20bubble%20burst%2C%20though%20I%20didn't%20let%20it%20get%20to%20me.%20It%20was%20not%20an%20arranged%20marriage%2C%20I%20was%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20that%20person.%20I%20have%20known%20him%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20I%20was%20married%20at%2016%2C%20had%20twins%20at%2017%20and%20got%20divorced%20at%2018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Furvashi-dholakia-on-repeating-clothes-we-are-under-constant-pressure-4265490%5C%22%3EUrvashi%20Dholakia%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20got%20candid%20about%20how%20supportive%20her%20parents%20were.%20She%20said%20after%20getting%20divorced%20at%2018%20years%20of%20age%2C%20she%20resumed%20working%20at%2019.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20supports%20you%20in%20your%20time%20of%20need%20more%20than%20your%20parents.%20I%20had%20to%20start%20back%20from%20scratch%20which%20is%20a%20different%20thing.%20The%20industry%20was%20always%20welcoming.%20Of%20course%2C%20people%20take%20your%20advantage.%20But%20I%20needed%20finance.%E2%80%9D%20When%20asked%20what%20led%20to%20her%20divorce%2C%20Urvashi%20Dholakia%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20didn't%20want%20the%20responsibility%20and%20fell%20out%20of%20love%2C%20but%20why%20would%20I%20have%20abandoned%20the%20two%20kids%3F%20If%20I%20had%20to%20do%20that%2C%20I%20would%20have%20not%20given%20birth%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20that%20her%20sons%C2%A0Sagar%20and%20Kshitij%20Dholakia%20have%20never%20met%20their%20father.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20don't%20want%20to%20know%20about%20him.%20We%20have%20tried%20to%20make%20them%20know%20about%20him%2C%20but%20they%20have%20always%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20don't%20want%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20hasn't%20spoken%20to%20her%20ex-husband%20since%20their%20divorce.%C2%A0%20Meanwhile%2C%20Urvashi%20Dholakia%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20the%20dance%20reality%20show%3Cem%3E%20Jhalak%20Dikhhla%20Jaa%2011.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702635000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4prlqd8_urvashi_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22