vernment%20of%20conspiring%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67725935%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67725935.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67725935.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nehru%20and%20Kashmir%3A%20After%20SC's%20Article%20370%20Order%2C%20BJP%20Attempts%26nbsp%3Bto%20Distort%20History%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F26170753%2FJawaharlal_Nehru_with_Sardar_Patelfinal.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-kashmir-article-370-verdict%5C%22%3Eupheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20RSS%20ideologues%20are%20celebrating%20it%20as%20a%20ratification%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20while%20leaders%20of%20parties%20based%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20aghast%20with%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20top%20court%20pronounced%20the%20order%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Famit-shah-says-nehrus-mistakes-on-kashmir-led-to-suffering-of-jk-people-2474809-2023-12-11%5C%22%3Evilify%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20yet%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Using%20selective%20and%20distorted%20history%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20has%20been%20promoting%20the%20narrative%20that%20had%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20handled%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%2C%20the%20problem%20would%20have%20been%20solved%20then%20and%20there.%20Adding%20to%20that%2C%20Shah%20stated%20that%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20declare%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20Pakistan%20was%20a%20Himalayan%20blunder%20and%20that%20granting%20special%20status%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20painted%20as%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20decision%20alone%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20mistake%20which%20led%20to%20a%20series%20of%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20accusations%20are%20far%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20events%20that%20unfolded.%20The%20attempt%20to%20show%20Nehru%20and%20Patel%20as%20having%20differing%20opinions%20on%20Kashmir%20is%20a%20figment%20of%20imagination%20which%20abuses%20the%20facts%20of%20history%20to%20the%20extreme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20it%20was%20due%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20Nehru%20(and%20Sheikh%20Abdullah)%20that%20Kashmir%20acceded%20to%20India.%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%20had%20refused%20to%20merge%20with%20India%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20Praja%20Parishad.%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20dealing%20with%20the%20integration%20of%20princely%20states%2C%20had%20enough%20on%20his%20plate.%20Rajmohan%20Gandhi%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EPatel%20a%20Life%3C%2Fem%3E%20points%20out%20that%20what%20Patel%20had%20in%20mind%20about%20Kashmir%20was%20to%20strike%20a%20bargain%3A%20to%20have%20Hyderabad%20for%20India%20and%20to%20let%20Pakistan%20have%20Kashmir.%20Rajmohan%20Gandhi%20cites%20a%20speech%20Patel%C2%A0delivered%20at%20the%20Bahauddin%20College%20in%20Junagadh%20following%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20merger%20with%20India%2C%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20agree%20to%20Kashmir%20if%20they%20agreed%20to%20Hyderabad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treaty%20of%20accession%20with%20India%20was%20signed%20by%20Maharaja%20Hari%20Singh%20after%20the%20marauding%20tribal%20militias%20launched%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20were%20close%20to%20Srinagar.%20He%20approached%20India%2C%20whose%20leaders%20sent%20the%20army%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20Kashmir%20accede%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fpublic-first-time-jammu-kashmirs-instrument-accession-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Backstory%20of%20Article%20370%3A%20A%20True%20Copy%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Instrument%20of%20Accession%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hari%20Singh%20fostered%20dreams%20of%20an%20Independent%20Kashmir%20and%20Patel%20was%20content%20with%20making%20sure%20that%20Hyderabad%20merges%20with%20India%2C%20it%20was%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%20who%20advocated%20that%20the%20region%20join%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20His%20consideration%20was%20not%20religion%20but%20the%20ideals%20of%20secularism%20and%20socialism.%20He%20was%20keen%20on%20land%20reforms%2C%20which%20he%20saw%20as%20an%20impossibility%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20the%20predominant%20leadership%20had%20a%20feudal%20mindset.%20With%20many%20Indian%20leaders%20talking%20socialism%2C%20he%20felt%20it%20was%20possible%20here.%20His%20belief%20in%20a%20secular%20India%20was%20based%20on%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20and%20other%20RSS%20ideologues%20say%20that%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20was%20faulty%20and%20was%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20British%20commanders%2C%20to%20whose%20opinion%20Nehru%20succumbed.%20This%20again%20is%20disproved%20by%20the%20facts%20of%20history.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20was%20the%20governor%20general%20of%20India.%20He%20advised%20a%20cease-fire%20and%20took%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%20He%20was%20not%20alone.%20The%20Indian%20leadership%20saw%20the%20consequences%20of%20extending%20the%20war%3A%20many%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20for%20the%20Indian%20army.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3ESardar%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20Correspondence%2C%201945-50%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20published%20in%201974%20by%20the%20Navjivan%20Publishing%20House%2C%20he%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Con%204%20June%201948%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Gopalswamy%20Ayyangar%2C%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98military%20position%20is%20not%20too%20good%2C%20and%20I%20am%20afraid%20that%20our%20military%20resources%20are%20strained%20to%20the%20utmost%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20So%20much%20for%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20false%20bravado%20that%20had%20the%20ceasefire%20not%20been%20declared%2C%20the%20whole%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20have%20been%20part%20of%20India!%20This%20is%20a%20concocted%20view%20that%20is%20not%20backed%20by%20historical%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20view%20that%20taking%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20UN%20was%20a%20historical%20blunder%2C%20let%20us%20again%20listen%20to%20Sardar%20Patel.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20specific%20issues%20raised%20by%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20you%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20question%20of%20Kashmir%20is%20before%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Nehru%20dated%20February%2023%2C%201950.%20And%20that%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20having%20invoked%20a%20forum%20to%20the%20settlement%20of%20disputes%20open%20to%20both%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20members%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Organization%2C%20nothing%20further%20need%20be%20done%20in%20the%20way%20of%20settlement%20of%20disputes%20than%20to%20leave%20matters%20to%20be%20adjusted%20through%20that%20forum.%E2%80%9D%20The%20letter%20is%20available%20in%20the%20tenth%20volume%20of%20%3Cem%3ESardar%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20Correspondence%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20called%20the%20Pakistan%20army%E2%80%99s%20actions%20in%20Kashmir%20an%20invasion%20and%20the%20resolution%20asked%20Pakistan%20to%20vacate%20the%20aggression%20while%20asking%20India%20to%20reduce%20the%20army%20to%20a%20minimum%20as%20a%20condition%20for%20a%20referendum.%20Pakistan%2C%20backed%20by%20US%20support%2C%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20its%20armies%20leading%20to%20a%20stalemate.%20And%20a%20referendum%2C%20to%20assess%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20people%2C%20could%20not%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnehru-prescient-apprehensions-jana-sangh-kashmir-bjp-modi%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20Has%20Confirmed%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Worries%20About%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20Divisive%20Plans%20for%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20blaming%20Nehru%20for%20Article%20370%20goes%2C%20the%20RSS%20combine%20deliberately%20forgets%20that%20Article%20370%20%E2%80%93%20which%20gave%20total%20autonomy%20to%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%20except%20in%20the%20matters%20of%20external%20affairs%2C%20defence%20and%20communication%20%E2%80%93%20was%20finalised%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20assembly%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20as%20home%20minister%2C%20was%20overseeing%20the%20drafting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20five%20months%20of%20negotiations%2C%20when%20the%20outline%20of%20what%20would%20become%20Article%20370%20had%20been%20decided%2C%20N.G.%20Iyengar%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20which%20is%20again%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20for%20people%20to%20verify.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20please%20let%20Jawaharlal%20Ji%20know%20directly%20that%20all%20these%20provisions%20are%20agreeable%20to%20you%E2%80%A6%20only%20after%20you%20agree%20will%20Nehru%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheopenview.in%2F2019%2F11%2F14%2Fsrinath-raghavan-busts-myths-around-nehrus-kashmir-policies%2F%5C%22%3Eissue%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Sheikh%20Abdullah%20that%20you%20(he)%20can%20go%20ahead.%E2%80%9D%20This%20shows%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20centrality%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distortion%20of%20history%20is%20a%20major%20tool%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20communal%20forces.%20While%20they%20have%20routinely%20been%20distorting%20medieval%20history%2C%20lately%20they%20have%20intensified%20distorting%20the%20history%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%20the%20events%20related%20to%20Kashmir.%20Through%20these%20efforts%2C%20driven%20by%20their%20vast%20propaganda%20machine%2C%20Nehru%20is%20criticised%20to%20the%20hilt%20and%20an%20attempt%20is%20made%20to%20create%20a%20binary%20between%20Patel%20and%20Nehru.%20Nehru%20is%20targeted%20because%20he%20stood%20rock%20solid%20against%20the%20communalism%20practised%20by%20Hindu%20nationalists.%20What%20is%20needed%20most%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20democratic%20norms%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20commitments%20which%20were%20given%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20region.%20Vilifying%20Nehru%20is%20no%20solution%20to%20this%20vexed%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702634420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F26170753%2FJawaharlal_Nehru_with_Sardar_Patelfinal.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnehru-kashmir-article-370-rss-bjp-distort-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attempt%20to%20show%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%20as%20having%20differing%20opinions%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Kashmir%20is%20a%20figment%20of%20imagination%20which%20abuses%20the%20facts%20of%20history%20to%20the%20extreme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnehru-kashmir-article-370-rss-bjp-distort-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi%20dealt%20with%20emotional%20challenge%20through%20Sridevi's%20work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702634360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106018807%2Cimgsize-41098.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhow