bir%20Purkayastha%2C%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20his%20latest%20book%20%3Ci%3EKeeping%20Up%20the%20Good%20Fight%3A%20From%20the%20Emergency%20to%20the%20Present%20Day%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20along%20with%20the%20portal%E2%80%99s%20Human%20Resources%20head%2C%20Amit%20Chakraborty.%20In%20October%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayastha-and-chakravarti-remanded-to-nine-day-police-custody%5C%22%3Ewere%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20a%20case%20registered%20under%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN.%20Ram%2C%20director%2C%20The%20Hindu%20Group%20Publishing%20Private%20Limited%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20event%20virtually%2C%20said%20the%20most%20interesting%20thing%20was%20the%20connection%20the%20book%20drew%20between%20the%20Emergency%20of%201975-77%2C%20during%20which%20Purkayastha%20was%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20for%20a%20year%2C%20and%20to%20what%20had%20happened%20in%20the%20present%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20much%20more%20serious%20attack%20in%20perhaps%20darker%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstitutions%20have%20been%20captured%2C%20institutions%20have%20been%20manipulated%2C%20and%20media%20freedom%20is%20under%20full-scale%20attack%E2%80%A6of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20still%20spaces%20where%20people%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ram%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fveteran-journalists-writers-take-part-in-panel-discussion-on-prabir-purkayasthas-new-book%2Farticle67639355.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20was%20a%20very%20disturbing%20period%20this%20year%20that%20he%20would%20refer%20to%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindutva%20authoritarian%20regime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20in%20the%20book%20for%20him%20was%20the%20lesson%20that%20today%20things%20might%20look%20bad%20for%20media%20freedom%20and%20for%20the%20basic%20human%20rights%20guaranteed%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20pessimistic%20about%20it%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CMay%20be%20short-term%20pessimism%20is%20inevitable%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20pessimistic%2C%20and%20this%20is%20not%20contrived%20or%20artificially%20communicated%20in%20the%20book%2C%20I%20think%20it%20comes%20through%20living%20the%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20observed%20that%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20the%20media%20had%20not%20performed%20well%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20adding%20that%20currently%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20media%20was%20under%20attack%3B%20journalists%20were%20being%20murdered%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20work%20and%20no%20justice%20rendered%3B%20and%20many%20had%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20UAPA.%20He%20was%20encouraged%20by%20the%20the%20support%20shown%20by%20numerous%20media%20organisations%20towards%20Purkayastha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20the%20whole%20McCarthyism%20campaign%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20essentially%20a%20media%20story%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20a%20complete%20socio-political%2C%20ideological%20formation%20which%20has%20injected%20a%20lot%20of%20poison%20into%20the%20information%20ecosystem.%20The%20McCarthyism%20that%20descended%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%2C%20particularly%20on%20Prabir%20and%20Amit%2C%20was%20aided%20and%20abetted%20by%20lousy%20piece%20of%20journalism%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20an%20article%20on%20American%20millionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-case-no-foreign-funding-neville-roy-singham-company-statement%5C%22%3ENeville%20Roy%20Singham%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15160512%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-15-at-4.02.53-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15160512%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-15-at-4.02.53-PM-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15160512%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-15-at-4.02.53-PM-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15160512%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-15-at-4.02.53-PM-1-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689342%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20book%20launch%20on%20Thursday.%20Photo%3A%20Shahid%20Tantray%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20book%20was%20a%20modern%20classic%20for%20him.%20He%20said%20he%20hoped%20that%20it%20appealed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cemoticon%E2%80%9D%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20as%20a%20nation%20tend%20to%20value%20our%20liberties%20so%20cheaply%20and%2C%20possibly%2C%20one%20reason%20is%20that%20we%20have%20people%20like%20Prabir%2C%20we%20have%20in%20this%20generation%20people%20like%20Umar%20Khalid..%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20these%20men%20and%20women%20of%20conscience%20who%20fight%20the%20good%20fight%2C%20or%20remind%20us%20that%20the%20constitution%20is%20a%20solemn%20compact%20between%20citizen%20and%20citizen%2C%20like%20this%20is%20a%20nation%20that%20we%20will%20work%20together%20and%20we%20will%20live%20together.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20Prabir%20has%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20defending%20the%20constitution%20twice%20in%20his%20lifetime%2C%E2%80%9D%20