Test%20Match%20on%20June%2025%2C%201932.%20The%20four-day%20Test%20match%20at%20Lord's%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20rich%20legacy%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%20A%20year%20later%20on%20December%2015%2C%20the%20team%2C%20led%20by%20Colonel%20CK%20Nayadu%2C%20played%20its%20first-ever%20Test%20Match%20on%20Indian%20soil%20against%20Douglas%20Jardine's%20England%20at%20the%20Bombay%20Gymkhana%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2090%20years%20of%20the%20historic%20day%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20today%20shared%20a%20picture%20on%20X%20of%20the%20first-ever%20Test%20match%20on%20Indian%20soil.%20%26quot%3BToday%20marks%20the%2090th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20first-ever%20cricket%20Test%20match%20played%20on%20Indian%20soil%2C%20India%20vs%20England%20at%20the%20historic%20Bombay%20Gymkhana%20ground%20on%2015%20December%201933%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Indians%20(%26amp%3Bdogs)%20were%20not%20allowed%20on%20the%20Gymkhana%20premises%20those%20days%2C%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Patiala%2C%20offended%20by%20the%20way%20his%20compatriots%20were%20treated%2C%20then%20established%20the%20Cricket%20Club%20of%20India%20and%20the%20adjoining%20Brabourne%20Stadium%2C%20in%20whose%20pavilion%20no%20racist%20restrictions%20applied.%20It%20was%20a%20great%20venue%20where%20I%20watched%20many%20a%20Test%20in%20my%20childhood%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20marks%20the%2090th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20first-ever%20cricket%20Test%20match%20played%20on%20Indian%20soil%2C%20India%20vs%20England%20at%20the%20historic%20Bombay%20Gymkhana%20ground%20on%2015%20December%201933.%20%5Bpic%5D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%20Indians%20(%26amp%3B%20dogs)%20were%20not%20allowed%20on%20the%20Gymkhana%20premises%20those%20days%2C%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Patiala%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1kCJP1M0MR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1kCJP1M0MR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(%40ShashiTharoor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%2Fstatus%2F1735567717229548024%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDouglas%20Jardine's%20English%20side%20was%20notoriously%20famous%20for%20its%20%26quot%3BBodyline%26quot%3B%20series%20during%20the%201932-33%20Ashes%20series%20against%20Australia%20to%20counter%20the%20batting%20skills%20of%20Sir%20Don%20Bradman%20and%20other%20Australian%20batters%20by%20pitching%20the%20ball%20at%20the%20batsman's%20body.%20England%20won%20the%201932-33%20%26quot%3BBodyline%20Ashes%26quot%3B%204-1.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20has%20been%20the%20traditional%20cricket%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20giving%20legends%20like%20Vijay%20Merchant%2C%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20Ajit%20Wadekar%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20Maharaja%20of%20Patiala%20Bhupinder%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20credited%20for%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20Indian%20team%2C%20created%20the%20Cricket%20Club%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20in%201933%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20BCCI.%20The%20famous%20Brabourne%20Stadium%2C%20which%20houses%20the%20CCI%20came%20into%20existence%20because%20of%20the%20discrimination%20the%20team%20faced%20at%20the%20Gymkhana%20Club.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Test%20match%20is%20special%20in%20many%20ways%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%20Events%20at%20the%20Bombay%20Gymkhana%20Club%20in%201933%20shaped%20the%20future%20years%20of%20the%20team%20and%20also%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20cricket%20club%20accessible%20to%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty%20years%20later%2C%20a%20dispute%20between%20the%20CCI%20and%20the%20Bombay%20Cricket%20Association%20(BCA)%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20iconic%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Iconic%20Test%20Match%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20first%2C%20India%20was%20bowled%20out%20for%20219%2C%20with%20Lala%20Amarnath%20being%20the%20leading%20run%20scorer%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%20England%20scored%20438%20in%20response%20and%20took%20a%20big%20lead%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Bryan%20Valentine's%20136%2C%20but%20Mohammad%20Nissar%2C%20the%20faster%20pre-independence%20bowler%20India%20has%20ever%20produced%2C%20took%20a%20five-wicket%20haul.%20Nissar%20and%20Amar%20Singh%2C%20the%20Indian%20bowling%20duo%20were%20considered%20as%20the%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20legendary%20all-rounder%20Lala%20Amarnath%20scored%20118%20in%20the%20second%20innings.%20He%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20score%20a%20test%20century%20and%20became%20the%20leading%20run%20scorer%20for%20India%20in%20Tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20won%20the%20test%20match%20by%209%20wickets%2C%20but%20undoubtedly%20the%20Test%20match%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20in%20India's%20rich%20cricketing%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702631040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fdcaj7i5_1933-test-match-_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-test-played-in-india-dogs-and-indians-werent-allowed-to-spectate-4678691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ninety-one%20years%20ago%2C%20an%20'All-India'%20cricket%20team%20travelled%20to%20England%20to%20play%20its%20first-ever%20Test%20Match%20on%20June%2025%2C%201932.%20The%20four-day%20Test%20match%20at%20Lord's%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20rich%20legacy%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-1st-test-played-in-india-dogs-and-indians-werent-allowed-to-spectate-4678691%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampprojec