articleshow%2F106016474.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Present%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20today%20at%20a%20grand%20event%20in%20Jaipur%20that%20was%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20first-time%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20was%20named%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20by%20the%20BJP%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20has%20two%20deputies%20-%20%26quot%3BPeople's%20princess%26quot%3B%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20who%20was%20an%20aspirant%20for%20the%20top%20post%20-%20and%20senior%20leader%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiya%20Kumari%20and%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20were%20sworn-in%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20immediately%20after%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20took%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oath%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20some%20BJP-ruled%20states%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20also%20attended%20the%20swearing-in.%20Mr%20Gehlot%20sat%20next%20to%20%26quot%3Brival%26quot%3B%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhwat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma's%20birthday%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2056-year-old%2C%20initially%20associated%20with%20the%20ABVP%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20has%20always%20kept%20a%20low%20profile.%20He%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20organisation%20man%20by%20party%20colleagues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20won%20115%20seats%20in%20the%20200-member%20Assembly%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20whose%20results%20were%2