Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Satyendar%20Jain%E2%80%99s%20petition%20for%20bail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20before%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fwill-not-control-the-judge-cji-refuses-to-defer-hearing-on-satyendar-jains-bail-plea-listed-before-another-bench-2810934%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Jain%2C%20said%20in%20front%20of%20the%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20bench%20that%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20deferred.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20case%20had%20originally%20been%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20A.S.%20Bopanna%2C%20and%20was%20later%20moved%20to%20Justice%20Trivedi%E2%80%99s%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20justice%20refused%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20control%20what%20the%20judge%20is%20doing%20in%20the%20matter%20listed%20before%20her.%20The%20judge%20who%20has%20the%20case%20will%20decide.%20I%20cannot.%20I%20cannot%20take%20a%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%206%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20on%20the%20question%20of%20case%20listing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20personally%20come%20across%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20listed%20before%20various%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20upon%20first%20listing%20and%2F%20or%20in%20which%20notice%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20being%20taken%20away%20from%20those%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20and%20listed%20before%20other%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches.%20Despite%20first%20coram%20being%20available%20the%20matters%20are%20being%20listed%20before%20a%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20in%20which%20second%20coram%20presides.%20Matters%20listed%20before%20Court%20No.%202%2C%204%2C%206%2C%207%20amongst%20others%20have%20been%20shifted%20out%20and%20listed%20before%20other%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20in%20clear%20disregard%20of%20the%20Rules%2C%20the%20Handbook%20on%20Practice%20and%20Office%20Procedure%20referred%20above%20and%20established%20Practice%20and%20Convention.%20Curiously%2C%20the%20Seniority%20of%20the%20first%20coram%20is%20also%20being%20ignored%20in%20doing%20so.%20Our%20attention%20is%20also%20been%20drawn%20by%20esteemed%20Colleagues%20at%20the%20Bar%2C%20Seniors%2C%20and%20Advocates%20on%20Record%20(AoRs)%2C%20about%20various%20cases%20in%20which%20they%20have%20appeared%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20later%20the%20matters%20being%20listed%20before%20different%20Benches.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20proper%20for%20me%20to%20enumerate%20these%20matters%20as%20many%20of%20them%20are%20pending%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-registry-isnt-listing-cases-the-way-it-is-supposed-to-a-letter-to-the-cji%5C%22%3EDave%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fprashant-bhushan-writes-to-sc-registrar-on-arbitrary-allocation-of-cases-to-justice-bela-m-trivedi%5C%22%3Ewrote%20to%20the%20registrar%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20questioning%20the%20way%20in%20which%20sensitive%20cases%20were%20being%20transferred%20to%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Trivedi.%20Bhushan%20specifically%20expressed%20concern%20about%20a%20batch%20of%20matters%20challenging%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20cases%20coming%20up%20before%20Justice%20Trivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fcontrary-to-sc-s-rules-of-assignment-at-least-8-politically-sensitive-cases-moved-to-one-judge-in-4-months-65713ae124602%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20highlighted%20the%20news%20about%20cases%20being%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20Justice%20Trivedi%2C%20reporting%20th