.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20the%20report%20provides%20percentages%20of%20people%20unable%20to%20afford%20a%20healthy%20diet%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%20(66%25)%2C%20Pakistan%20(82%25)%2C%20Iran%20(30%25)%2C%20China%20(11)%25%2C%20Russia%20(2.6%25)%2C%20the%20US%20(1.2%25)%2C%20and%20the%20UK%20(0.4%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Agricultural%20Organisation%20(FAO)%20released%20the%20report%20amid%20criticism%20from%20food%20security%20advocates%20and%20nutrition%20experts%20who%20say%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fscale-of-hunger-in-india-three-of-four-indians-underfed-says-united-nations%2Fcid%2F1986963%5C%22%3EIndian%20government%20is%20denying%20food%20deprivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20poor%20nutrition%20issues%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20challenged%20the%20FAO%20report%E2%80%99s%20estimate%20of%2016.6%25%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20based%20on%20a%20survey%20with%20a%20small%20sample%20size%20and%20biased%20methodology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20collected%20from%20a%20minuscule%20sample%20for%20a%20country%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20size%20has%20been%20used%20to%20compute%20the%20proportion%20of%20undernourished%20(population%20in)%20India%20which%20is%20not%20only%20wrong%20and%20unethical%2C%20it%20also%20reeks%20of%20obvious%20bias%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-coming-misadventure-with-rice-fortification-in-all-food-schemes%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Coming%20Misadventure%20With%20Rice%20Fortification%20in%20All%20Food%20Schemes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20experts%20see%20a%20contradiction%20between%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20the%20FAO%20estimate%20that%2016.6%25%20%E2%80%94%20200%20million%20people%2C%20even%20under%20the%202011%20census%20%E2%80%94%20are%20undernourished%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20estimate%20that%20around%20813%20million%20people%20require%20food%20assistance%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fscale-of-hunger-in-india-three-of-four-indians-underfed-says-united-nations%2Fcid%2F1986963%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20approved%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY)%20%E2%80%93%20that%20provides%205kg%20free%20food%20grain%20per%20family%20per%20month%20covering%20813%20million%20people%20%E2%80%93%20for%20five%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign%2C%20a%20non-government%20network%20campaigning%20for%20food%20security%2C%20said%20the%20FAO%20estimate%20that%201.043%20billion%20people%20could%20not%20afford%20a%20healthy%20diet%20was%20in%20line%20with%20their%20own%20assessment%20that%20over%20a%20billion%20people%20need%20food%20aid%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20813%20million%20estimate%20is%20based%20on%20the%202011%20census%20%E2%80%94%20the%20next%20census%20is%20overdue%20by%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raj%20Shekhar%2C%20national%20coordinator%20with%20the%20RFC%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fscale-of-hunger-in-india-three-of-four-indians-underfed-says-united-nations%2Fcid%2F1986963%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20the%20new%20census%2C%20many%20needy%2C%20vulnerable%20people%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20ration%20cards%20that%20will%20entitle%20them%20to%20the%20PMGKAY%20benefits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20based%20on%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%202021%20found%20that%20among%20the%20poorest%2020%25%20households%2C%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20women%2C%20even%20pregnant%20women%2C%20did%20not%20consume%20dairy%20products.%20It%20also%20found%20that%20over%2050%25%20of%20women%20and%2040%25%20of%20men%20in%20the%20country%20did%20not%20consume%20vitamin-A-rich%20fruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES.V.%20Subramanian%2C%20professor%20of%20population%20health%20and%20geography%20at%20Harvard%20University%2C%20who%20led%20the%20study%2C%20said%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20own%20count%20of%20813%20million%20people%20needing%20food%20aid%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbit%20of%20a%20surprise%E2%80%9D%20because%20%E2%80%9Cit%20seems%20larger%20than%20what%20is%20suggested%20by%20conventional%20measures%20of%20undernutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3Edenied%20India%E2%80%99s%20low%20ranking%20on%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20well.%20It%20had%20called%20the%20exercise%20%E2%80%9Can%20erroneous%20measure%20of%20hunger%20with%20serious%20methodological%20issues%E2%80%9D%20that%20displayed%20%E2%80%9Ca%20malafide%20intent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702618628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24212038%2FIMG_2670.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-74-indians-unable-to-afford-healthy-diet-un-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20also%20estimated%20India%E2%80%99s%20proportion%20of%20undernourished%20population%20at%2016.6%25%20during%202020-2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-74-indians-unable-to-afford-healthy-diet-un-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222023%20sees%20worst-ever%20Israel-Hamas%20combat%20as%20Russian%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%20grind%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702618147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstat